**Privacy Policy**

Watermelon ("the Bot") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how your personal information is collected, used, and disclosed by the Bot.

**Information We Collect**

The Bot collects the following information when you use it:
- User ID
- Messages (only when needed for bot functionality)

**How We Use Your Information**

We use the collected information to:
- Provide bot services
- Improve bot functionality
- Respond to user queries

**Data Retention**

We retain your data only for as long as necessary to provide the bot services. Once it is no longer needed, we will delete your data.

**Sharing Your Information**

We do not share your information with third parties.

**Contact Us**

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at michalih@icloud.com.

**Changes to This Privacy Policy**

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
